" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 473px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Nomogram for determining body mass index",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 453px; height: 511px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The nomogram is used by placing a ruler or other straight edge between the body weight in kilograms or pounds (the left-hand line) and the height in centimeters or inches (the right-hand line). The body mass index is read from the middle of the scale, in metric units.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
